data.description: Terrific 4/3/3 High performance home. Downstairs offers: Master bedroom with open fireplace to a lush Master bath. Open concept. Kitchen with tons of Granite counter space & Stainless Appliances. Living area with Fireplace and lots of windows. Large Guest bedroom with full bath or private office. Plus bonus area making 2nd office potential. While the upstairs has 3 bedrooms, Pullman bath and Game room. Full Brick Private Street. Desirable location-Broken Arrow schools, close to turnpike and trails.
